<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figure 6. Aspidophorodon longicornutum Qiao &amp; Xu sp. nov. Apterous viviparous female A dorsal view of head B antenna C marginal processes of thoracic nota and abdominal tergites I-IV D ultimate rostral segment E oval sculptures of abdominal tergites F marginal process of abdominal tergite IV G siphunculus H spinal seta of abdominal tergite VIII I cauda J anal plate K genital plate. Scale bars: 0.10 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1106.77912.figure6" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/702341" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">6G</figureCitation>
